      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">When to Play GI (SOWPODS Games Only)</h2>

      <p>GI is a low-scoring word. Its value comes from tactical board positioning, not raw points:</p>

