        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">G-tile dump:</span> When your rack is clogged with consonants and no longer G words are available, GI lets you dump G quickly. I is the second most common tile (9 copies), so there's usually an I on the board to hook onto.</p>
        </div>
